00:00:02.240 --> 00:00:06.200
Here, this is my Shrimp and Shimeji mushroom pasta 
with tomato cream sauce.

00:00:06.230 --> 00:00:08.050
It's my favorite recipe.

00:00:08.090 --> 00:00:10.000
Enjoy my taste.

00:00:10.030 --> 00:00:12.290
