00:00:12.330 --> 00:00:14.510
Hello, everyone.

00:00:14.550 --> 00:00:18.730
Today, I'm going to make "Shrimp and Shimeji mushroom 
pasta with tomato cream sauce".

00:00:18.770 --> 00:00:23.720
I really like tomato cream that is easy and delicious.
I often cook it for lunch.

00:00:23.750 --> 00:00:29.480
By heating a tomato makes it mild taste.
And more fresh cream makes the sauce rich.

00:00:29.510 --> 00:00:32.150
The ingredients are as follows;

00:00:32.180 --> 00:00:35.990
Dried pasta, today I use 1.4mm thin tipe.

00:00:35.990 --> 00:00:43.640
De-veined shrimp, Shimeji mushroom, Tomato sauce
Fresh cream, Salt, White wine and...

00:00:43.640 --> 00:00:46.330
Basil leaf for decoration.

00:00:46.370 --> 00:00:48.640
So let's get started.

00:00:48.680 --> 00:00:50.670
So, let's get started.

00:00:50.700 --> 00:00:55.470
First of all, 
add salt to boiled water.

00:00:55.500 --> 00:01:00.230
Add a generous amount.

00:01:00.590 --> 00:01:03.990
Add the pasta into it.

00:01:04.020 --> 00:01:08.290
Twist the pasta and place into the pot.

00:01:08.820 --> 00:01:11.490
Sink the pasta into the boiled water.

00:01:11.530 --> 00:01:13.750
When all the pasta has sinked...

00:01:13.840 --> 00:01:16.480
Boil for 4 minutes.

00:01:16.510 --> 00:01:20.730
While boiling the pasta,
cook the other ingredients.

00:01:20.770 --> 00:01:27.010
This is a frying pan that has poured olive oil.
Turn on gas.

00:01:27.050 --> 00:01:31.340
After the frying pan has heated,
add the shrimps.

00:01:31.370 --> 00:01:34.980
They has deveined.

00:01:39.010 --> 00:01:46.770
When the both side have fried,
add the Shimeji mushrooms.

00:01:48.410 --> 00:01:53.340
When the oil has spread to all ingredients,
add the remaining ingredients.

00:01:53.380 --> 00:01:58.820
Add the white wine.

00:02:00.930 --> 00:02:06.760
Add the tomato sauce.

00:02:07.940 --> 00:02:15.570
This is the fresh cream.

00:02:31.250 --> 00:02:38.610
Season the sauce with salt.

00:02:38.650 --> 00:02:45.560
4 minutes have passed.
Add the pasta to the frying pan.

00:02:54.130 --> 00:02:58.230
Heat by frying pan for remaining 1 minute.

00:03:08.490 --> 00:03:14.200
Adjust the sauce hardness by the cooking liquid.

00:03:24.910 --> 00:03:28.050
When the sauce has spread to all ingredients,
 it's ready.

00:03:28.610 --> 00:03:30.840
Turn off the heat.

00:03:30.870 --> 00:03:33.710
Place on a serving dish.

00:03:38.840 --> 00:03:45.300
Twist the pasta and put on it.

00:03:49.400 --> 00:03:53.090
Finally,
place the Basil leaf for decoration.

00:03:53.630 --> 00:04:03.310
Break the Basil with your hands.
In doing so, you can get good aroma.

00:04:04.640 --> 00:04:08.320
And then,
it's ready.

00:04:08.360 --> 00:04:13.170
Here, my pasta is ready to be served.

00:04:13.200 --> 00:04:15.650
It's my favorite recipe.

00:04:15.690 --> 00:04:17.680
Enjoy my taste.

00:04:17.710 --> 00:04:21.710
So delicious.

